title: Panel: The Story by Investors in Startups
description: Join leading investors as they share insights on the startup ecosystem in Lebanon and the MENA region. Learn about investment trends, what investors look for in startups, and success stories from the region.

title: Building the Future: AI and Intelligent Systems
description: Explore the cutting-edge developments in AI and machine learning. From generative AI to MLOps, discover how AI is transforming industries and learn practical approaches to implementing AI solutions.

title: From Automation to Autonomy: The Future of Intelligent Cloud Systems
description: Modern cloud platforms automate deployments, scaling, and monitoring, yet they still depend on humans to interpret alerts, identify root causes, and take action. This talk will explore the next evolution of DevOps: autonomous cloud systems that can observe, reason, and act intelligently to maintain stability and performance.

title: Cross-Platform Mobile Development with Flutter
description: Dive into modern mobile app development with Flutter. Learn about clean architecture, state management, and building scalable mobile applications that work across platforms.

title: Modern Web Development: From React to Next.js
description: Explore the latest trends in frontend development. Learn about React, Next.js, modern build tools, and how to create engaging user experiences in web applications.

title: Algorithms and Data Structures: From Theory to Practice
description: Master the fundamentals of computer science with practical applications. Learn optimization techniques, graph theory, and how to solve complex computational problems efficiently.

title: Enterprise Architecture and Scalable Systems
description: Learn how to design and build enterprise-grade systems that scale. Covering microservices, database architecture, and building robust platforms for modern organizations.

title: Building Tech Communities: The .NET Lebanon Story
description: Discover how to build and nurture tech communities. Learn from the experience of founding the first .NET community in Lebanon and creating sustainable tech ecosystems.

title: From Idea to Impact: Entrepreneurship in Tech
description: Join successful entrepreneurs and learn about building tech startups, overcoming challenges, and creating meaningful impact in the technology sector.
